  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To compare the efficacy of SMP-114 versus placebo in terms of the percentage of patients meeting the ACR criteria for 20% improvement in RA (ACR20) at Week 24.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>To compare efficacy of SMP-114 versus placebo after 24 weeks in terms of ACR50, ACR70, DAS28 and EULAR response.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>To compare the efficacy of SMP-114 versus placebo in terms of change in core variables, time to response, Quality of Life, radiological measurements of joint damage, assessment of safety and tolerability, and PK measurements</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
